# Server-side secrets for the Supabase Edge Functions.
#
# Copy this file to supabase/.env.local and fill in the values you have. That
# file is gitignored (.env*.local) — never commit real keys, and never put any
# of these into an EXPO_PUBLIC_* variable: EXPO_PUBLIC_* values are bundled into
# the client app, these are server-only secrets.
#
# Only ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is required (humanize/alternatives). Every detector key
# below is OPTIONAL: a provider turns itself on only when its key is present, and
# /detect falls back to the built-in heuristic when none are set. Deploy never
# fails for a missing detector key.

# --- Required ---------------------------------------------------------------
# Anthropic API key for /humanize and /alternatives. Use a freshly-issued key.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Optional: real AI detectors for /detect --------------------------------
# See DETECTOR-INTEGRATION-PLAN.md. Set only the providers you have; the rest
# stay off and /detect uses whichever are configured (or the heuristic).

# GPTZero (primary provider). GPTZERO_VERSION optionally pins the model.
GPTZERO_API_KEY=
GPTZERO_VERSION=

# Originality.ai. ORIGINALITY_MODEL_VERSION optionally pins the AI model.
ORIGINALITY_API_KEY=
ORIGINALITY_MODEL_VERSION=

# Copyleaks (needs BOTH the API key and the account email to turn on).
# COPYLEAKS_SENSITIVITY optionally pins detection strictness (1-3).
COPYLEAKS_API_KEY=
COPYLEAKS_EMAIL=
COPYLEAKS_SENSITIVITY=
